UNITED STATES v. GABRIEL et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. January 22, 1901.) No. 2,793. Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. For opinion below, see 99 Fed. 716. D. Frank Lloyd, Asst. U. S. Atty. W. Wickham Smith, for appellees.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and SHIPMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed in open court.
